formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
Note-1					
AVS Corporation has opened Designated Bank Account (RERA Bank Account) mentioned as above. As it is informed to us by pertners of firm that it was initial phase for registering itself under RERA and they were in ambiguity and there was no clarity regarding transactions to be made with the Designated Bank Account (RERA Bank Account) , hence no amount has been deposited in designated bank account up to 31.12.2017. The Amount withdrawn from the bank, represent members collection received and deposited in normal bank account and Utilized for construction expenses as well as deposited in RERA bank account and withdrawn from the same.					
					
Note-2					
The firm has revised the estimation of land cost as the firm has paid Rs. 1,15,58,404/- for the project to the land owners for non-utilisation of FSI cost as per debit note raised by the land owners.					
					
Note-3					
Statement of Calculation of receivables from real estate project showing KYC Id which has not been verified by us. The said statement is as certified by authorised persons of M/s AVS Corporation.
